faq_1321.content:
**A:** Create custom agent types:

```javascript
// Define custom agent capabilities
mcp__claude-flow__daa_agent_create({
  agent_type: "custom-analyzer",
  capabilities: ["static-analysis", "performance-profiling", "security-scan"],
  resources: {
    memory: "2GB",
    cpu: "2"
  }
})

// Match capabilities to tasks
mcp__claude-flow__daa_capability_match({
  task_requirements: ["analyze-code", "find-vulnerabilities"],
  available_agents: ["custom-analyzer", "code-reviewer", "security-specialist"]
})
```

